facts.fact_text: Foreign direct investment (FDI) inflows increased from 13.1 million dollars in 1990 to 38.0 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Remittances in dollars as a proportion of total GDP (percent)
facts.fact_text: In 2018, the inflow of personal remittances was 3.9 % of GDP , down from 5.2 % in 1990

facts.seriesTitle: Debt service as a proportion of exports of goods and services (percent)
facts.fact_text: Debt service as a proportion of exports of goods and services increased from 1.6 % in 1990 to 2.0% in 2016.

facts.seriesTitle: Fixed Internet broadband subscriptions (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: Fixed-broadband internet penetration reached 0.0 per 100 inhabitants in 2003 to 1.6 per 100 inhabitants in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Internet users  (per 100 inhabitants)
facts.fact_text: The number of Internet users per 100 inhabitants increased from 2.1 in 2000 to 25.7 in 2017.

facts.seriesTitle: Total official development assistance (gross disbursement) for technical cooperation (millions of 2018 dollars)
facts.fact_text: The total gross disbursement of official development assistance for technical cooperation in constant prices of 2018 increased from 9.1 million dollars in 2000 to 18.8 million dollars in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, most-favoured-nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with most-favoured-nation status declined from 12.9 % in 2005 to 8.1% in 2015.

facts.seriesTitle: Worldwide weighted tariff-average, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The worldwide weighted tariff-average for countries with preferential status declined from 12.8 % in 2005 to 8.1% in 2015.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, most-favored nation status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average most-favored nation status tariff applied by developed countries was 2.7 % in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Average tariff applied by developed countries, preferential status (percent)
facts.fact_text: The average preferential status tariff applied by developed countries declined from 1.5 % in 2000 to 0.1% in 2018.

facts.seriesTitle: Dollar value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries (million dollars)
facts.fact_text: The value of all resources made available to strengthen statistical capacity in developing countries was 23.6 thousand dollars in 2017.
